column1: imbë (or imbe) is a word with two different meanings.
The Quenya word imbë (or imbe) means "between".
i falmalinnar imbë met, ar hísië (on the foaming waves between us
Helge Fauskanger has suggested that the word likely is Quenya.Helge Fauskanger
